---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Support"
  description="Support for Food Scanner, Glasshole, and companion apps from Scaling Human."
  path="/support.html"
>
  <article class="container prose">
    <header class="page-header">
      <p class="page-header__kicker">Help</p>
      <h1 class="page-header__title">Support</h1>
      <p class="page-header__lead">
        For help with Food Scanner, Glasshole, or the companion apps, contact the
        channels below.
      </p>
    </header>

    <p class="updated">Last updated: July 8, 2026</p>

    <ul>
      <li>
        Email:
        <a href="mailto:srikantha.ballani@gmail.com"
          >srikantha.ballani@gmail.com</a
        >
      </li>
      <li>
        GitHub:
        <a
          href="https://github.com/scalinghuman/experiments"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >https://github.com/scalinghuman/experiments</a
        >
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Compatibility</h2>
    <p>
      The iOS apps are iPhone apps and require iOS 26.0 or later.
    </p>
    <p>
      Glasshole supports Apple Intelligence on compatible iPhone models. Other
      supported iPhones can use configured cloud, local-network, PocketPal, or
      custom providers. Food Scanner’s default Local iPhone Vision mode works on
      supported iPhones without an API key.
    </p>

    <h2>Food Scanner</h2>
    <p>
      Food Scanner can be used without companion hardware by choosing a food
      photo from iPhone or taking a new iPhone camera photo. The optional
      companion APK can capture a food image and send it to the iOS app over
      local Wi-Fi or iPhone Personal Hotspot.
    </p>
    <p>
      Nutrition values are AI estimates for general information only, not medical
      advice.
    </p>

    <h2>Glasshole</h2>
    <p>
      Glasshole can be used without companion hardware by tapping the microphone
      button in the iOS app. The optional companion APK can start and stop
      real-time conversation capture and display AI-powered fact-check overlays
      after analysis.
    </p>
    <p>
      Use Glasshole only with the consent of everyone being recorded and in
      compliance with local laws and regulations where you use it.
    </p>

    <h2>Common Setup</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Install the iOS app from the App Store.</li>
      <li>Install the companion APK from GitHub.</li>
      <li>Connect the companion hardware to your iPhone Personal Hotspot.</li>
      <li>Open the iOS app and confirm the connection indicator.</li>
    </ol>
    <p>
      Companion setup may require ADB and manual voice-command registration.
    </p>

    <div class="links-row">
      <a href="/privacy.html">Privacy Policy</a>
      <a href="/apps/foodscanner">Food Scanner</a>
      <a href="/apps/glasshole">Glasshole AI</a>
      <a href="/">Home</a>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
